@startuml
title Sequences - Routes systeme et techniques

scale max 1050 width
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam pageMargin 10
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 10
skinparam sequenceMessageFontSize 9
skinparam sequenceParticipantFontSize 10
actor "Visiteur" as Visiteur
actor "Developpeur" as Dev
participant "Route web" as Web
participant "Vue welcome" as Welcome
participant "API Laravel" as API
participant "BackupController" as Backup
participant "mysqldump" as Dump
database "Base pharmacy" as DB
collections "storage" as Storage
participant "Migrations" as Migrations

== Accueil web ==
Visiteur -> Web : GET /
Web -> Welcome : view welcome
Welcome --> Web : HTML
Web --> Visiteur : page accueil

== Sauvegarde SQL publique ==
Visiteur -> API : GET /api/backup
API -> Backup : backup()
Backup -> Backup : generer nom backup date
Backup -> Dump : mysqldump --user=root pharmacy
Dump -> DB : lire schema et donnees
DB --> Dump : contenu SQL
Dump -> Storage : ecrire backup.sql
Storage --> Backup : fichier pret
Backup --> API : download et deleteFileAfterSend
API --> Visiteur : fichier SQL

== Migration incoherente observee ==
Dev -> Migrations : lire add_image_to_produits_table
Migrations -> DB : ALTER TABLE produits ADD image
DB --> Migrations : echec probable si produits absente
Migrations --> Dev : table medicaments possede deja image

@enduml
